Malice patted her on the back and stood up, the child in his arms. 
"Lets go inside."
He turns and goes inside, his tail off the ground.  He enters the 
mess hall once again and set the young bot in a chair.  He pulls up a 
chair and sits in front of her.
"No one is going to be angy with you.  Your friend is getting th best 
help here, and will be alright."
Malice got up and got the child a cup of energon and hande it to 
her.  He felt sorry for her, he felt the same way on a few occasions.
